# Skill-curator runtime state (written on-box by the agent's skill curator, not
# source). Keeping these out of git stops them showing as untracked drift and
# prevents an accidental commit of box-local state. Only the dot-prefixed state
# artifacts are listed; real skills (non-dotted dirs under skills/) stay tracked.
skills/.archive/
skills/.curator_backups/
skills/.curator_state
skills/.hub/
skills/.bundled_manifest
skills/.usage.json
skills/.usage.json.lock
